OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,FRecommendations from a newly launched
OL,8,Fcommission into social care will be
OL,9,F"doomed to failure" unless the true
OL,10,Fcost of inaction in the sector is set
OL,11,Fout, MPs have warned.
OL,13,FThe Health and Social Care Committee
OL,14,Fsaid there needs to be a "robust
OL,15,Ffinancial case" laid out for reform,
OL,16,Fto support the moral case, which it
OL,17,Fsaid has "never been stronger".
OL,19,FThe report comes just days after the
OL,20,Fformal launch of the Casey Commission
OL,21,Finto adult social care.
