OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,FIn their report, published on Monday,
OL,8,FMPs said #32 billion was spent on
OL,9,Fadult social care in the year to March
OL,10,F2024, and that there is "unsustainable
OL,11,Fpressure" on local authorities amid
OL,12,Fthe "high price for a failing system".
OL,14,FThe MPs set out what they described as
OL,15,Fvarious "unaccounted-for costs of
OL,16,Finaction", including some two million
OL,17,Fpeople aged 65 and over as well as 1.5
OL,18,Fmillion people of working-age not
OL,19,Fgetting the care they require.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@IO]tD@EOUtD@eO]wD@IOUxD@IO]
