OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,FThey warned of the "unknowable, and
OL,8,Fpotentially life-changing" charges for
OL,9,Fcare people face, including one in
OL,10,Fseven older people with costs
OL,11,Fexceeding #100,000.
OL,13,FThe report said 1.5 million unpaid
OL,14,Fcarers are providing more than 50
OL,15,Fhours of care weekly, with many having
OL,16,Fto cut hours or quit jobs entirely as
OL,17,Fa result, while care workers remain
OL,18,Funderpaid and twice as likely to be
OL,19,Fclaiming benefits as other workers.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@ZO]
