OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,FThe MPs also warned that local
OL,8,Fauthority budgets are "buckling under
OL,9,Fthe pressure of adult social care" and
OL,10,Fthe care provider market is "in
OL,11,Fdistress" as it struggles to cover
OL,12,Fcosts including underfunded recent
OL,13,Fincreases in the National Living Wage
OL,14,Fand National Insurance.
OL,16,FBut the report concluded that the
OL,17,FGovernment "does not have a robust
OL,18,Funderstanding of the extent of the
OL,19,Fcurrent system's failings" or good
OL,20,Fquality data on the outcomes of
OL,21,Fdelivering high quality care.
