OL,7,FAll recommendations "must remain
OL,8,Faffordable", the Government has said,
OL,9,F"operating within the fiscal
OL,10,Fconstraints of Spending Review
OL,11,Fsettlements for the remainder of this
OL,12,FParliament".
OL,14,FThe health and social care committee
OL,15,Fhas called on the Government to
OL,16,Fcommission research to fully quantify
OL,17,Fthe cost of doing nothing on adult
OL,18,Fsocial care reform ` including costs
OL,19,Fto unpaid carers, care workers,
OL,20,Fcouncils, care providers, the NHS and
OL,21,Fthe overall economy.
