OL,7,FCommittee chairwoman Layla Moran said
OL,8,Fsocial care is rarely discussed as a
OL,9,Fdriver of economic activity but that
OL,10,Fit has "enormous potential" to
OL,11,Fcontribute to the Government's wider
OL,12,Faims for economic growth and
OL,13,Femployment.
OL,15,FShe said: "In our inquiry, we heard
OL,16,Fthat an investment of #6.1 billion
OL,17,Fwould provide full economic benefits
OL,18,Fof #10.7 billion ` a return on
OL,19,Finvestment of 175%."
