OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,F"We want this report to change the
OL,8,Fnarrative on social care, and to act
OL,9,Fas a catalyst for building a strong
OL,10,Fand long-lasting case for reform. It
OL,11,Fmight seem that reforms will be costly
OL,12,Fand difficult, but continuing with
OL,13,Finaction will cost us all more."
OL,15,FCare minister Stephen Kinnock said:
OL,16,F"We are grateful for the committee's
OL,17,Fwork and will respond formally in due
OL,18,Fcourse.
