OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,F"Far from inaction, this Government
OL,8,Fhas hit the ground running on social
OL,9,Fcare. We inherited a social care
OL,10,Fsystem in crisis and took immediate
OL,11,Faction with our Plan for Change ` with
OL,12,Fa funding boost of up to #3.7 billion,
OL,13,Fan extra 15,000 home adaptations for
OL,14,Fdisabled people, a #2,000 uplift to
OL,15,FCarer's Allowance, and the first ever
OL,16,FFair Pay Agreement for care workers.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
