OL,3,CMPs warn social care reforms 'doomed
OL,4,Cto fail' without 'robust financial
OL,5,Ccase'
OL,7,F"A lot has been done, but we know
OL,8,Fthere is so much more to do and deep
OL,9,Freform is needed. That's why we
OL,10,Fappointed Baroness Louise Casey to
OL,11,Flead the independent commission
OL,12,Fworking to transcend party politics
OL,13,Fand build consensus on the future of
OL,14,Fadult social care, with her first
OL,15,Freport out next year."
OL,17,FThe Liberal Democrats said "delay is
OL,18,Fno longer an option" and that there
OL,19,Fcould not be a "starker contrast"
OL,20,Fbetween the Government's approach and
OL,21,Fthe committee's findings.
