OL,7,FHelen Morgan, the Lib Dem social care
OL,8,Fspokesperson, said: "Now it has been
OL,9,Flaid out in black and white that
OL,10,Finaction is untenable, the Government
OL,11,Fmust see sense and approach social
OL,12,Fcare reform with the urgency it
OL,13,Fdemands.
OL,15,F"To do anything less would be an
OL,16,Faffront to taxpayers who are currently
OL,17,Ffooting this monstrous bill for a
OL,18,Fbroken system which then only too
OL,19,Foften fails them in their time of need.
